I can tell you lots of things. Things on the city, kindred, displines, things to do, places to aviod and much more. What do you seek to know about?

Ahh displines are those special talents we learn as vampires. Some come naturally to us based on our clan others we can learn should be we be able to find a teacher willing to teach us. But be warned not all clans will teach their displines to you.

In order to learn a higher level of a displine you need one very basic thing Blood points. Dependant upon which level of the displine you are wanting to learn will depend on how much blood it will cost you. The more prefected you are to learning a displine the more blood points you will need to learn them.

Then you must find a teacher willing to teach you that displine. They will agree to be your mentor then and you may then learn what displine they are willing to let you learn. It of course will cost the same blood points as learning normal clan powers as well. Should you gain someone willing to let you learn their gift I can some times aid you along the way in learning those displines.
I can only aid you with the very basic displines. Animalism, Auspex, Celerity, Domanite, fortitude, obfuscate, potence, and presence.

Ahh well your undead now. Your life, as it is, is linked to blood and how much damage you take. Not all the elders reside in this location. Some go up stairs every now and then. But do be careful up stairs this darkness is sure to bring about Inquisitors.

Yes they are one of two groups that hunt our kind. How they found out about us is beyond me but they know and they seek to destroy us, these are the inquisitors. But there are also the garou. Wolves that have many forms and were made to hunt and kill us. They like us have their own special talents all geared towards ending unlives like ours. Be sure to be careful.
I see no one who is clanless...
